<div class="how-it-works">
    <h1>How It Works?</h1>
    <div class="steps-container">
        <div class="step-box">
            <h2>1Ô∏è‚É£ Upload an Image</h2>
            <p>Capture or upload a clear image of the waste item using your device. Ensure that the waste is properly visible and centered in the frame with white background(prefrable) to help the system analyze it more accurately.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-box">
            <h2>2Ô∏è‚É£ AI-Based Analysis</h2>
            <p>Our intelligent AI model processes the uploaded image using advanced image recognition techniques and classifies it into one of the predefined waste categories such as plastic, paper, e-waste, etc.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-box">
            <h2>3Ô∏è‚É£ Get Instant Results</h2>
            <p>Based on the AI prediction, the system instantly displays the waste type along with additional classification details. For best accuracy, use images with plain white or clutter-free backgrounds.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-box">
            <h2>4Ô∏è‚É£ Learn About Waste Disposal</h2>
            <p>Along with the classification result, the system provides detailed guidance on how to dispose of or recycle the item properly according to its type, encouraging responsible environmental practices.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
</div>


<section class="why-recycling-matters">
    <h1>Why Recycling Matters?</h1>
    <p>Recycling is essential for protecting our environment and building a more sustainable world. It reduces the burden on landfills, preserves valuable resources, lowers greenhouse gas emissions, and minimizes environmental pollution caused by improper waste disposal.</p>
    <div class="recycling-benefits">
        <div class="benefit-box">
            <h2>üåç Environmental Protection</h2>
            <p>Recycling reduces the need for raw material extraction, decreases land and water pollution, and significantly lowers harmful emissions, playing a direct role in preserving biodiversity and natural ecosystems.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-box">
            <h2>üí∞ Economic Benefits</h2>
            <p>By creating employment opportunities in collection, processing, and recycling industries, recycling contributes to economic growth while also saving money on waste disposal and raw material production.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-box">
            <h2>üîÑ Energy Conservation</h2>
            <p>Manufacturing products using recycled materials requires significantly less energy than producing them from scratch, leading to lower energy consumption and a reduced environmental footprint.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


